                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>17 <sic>tober</sic> 54</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Enclosed please find<lb/> seven dollars 37 cts amount of 4\n                (larger<lb/> size) prayer books sent less Express<lb/> charges as per a/c enclosed.\n                I hope to<lb/> sell the small ones soon but would not<lb/> wait to remit you,\n                although the books<lb/> are not yet paid for. I send by Express<lb/> because the\n                post is not safe. I once<lb/> remitted to <persName>Moss &amp; Bro.</persName> In\n                your city a small<lb/> amount which went where perhaps you<lb/> and <persName>Mr\n                    Newhouses</persName> new <add>?</add> are. <persName>Mrs<lb/> Cohen</persName>\n                sent a dollar in a letter to <persName>Sarah<lb/> Joseph</persName> a couple of\n                weeks since, that also<lb/> has been <hi rend=\"underline\">geganavd</hi><add>?</add>\n                as a worthy Bar<lb/> Tismel here is accustomed to say. It will<lb/> cost you little\n                more than post charges.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">It trust you have by this<lb/> time received the copy of my\n                father's<lb/> work on the “Melodies” which was ordered<lb/> to be sent you from\n                    <placeName>New York</placeName>. The <placeName>London</placeName><lb/> press\n                musical &amp; literary critics have<lb/> spoken in the highest terms of the\n                books<lb/> and pronounced the melodies incomparably<lb/> solemn. Many of these\n                melodies have</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p38c9rq44/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
