                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>costing 25 cents put me out of <add>?</add><lb/> with such a notion.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">There is nothing stirring here<lb/> worth writing about. I hope\n                your<lb/> synagogue gives a head and proves<lb/> that there is plenty of room\n                for<lb/> two or even three for the Portuguese<lb/> Minhag in these days of\n                Minhag<lb/> America</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I remain yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Abraham de Sola</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
